1
00:00:00,310 --> 00:00:01,670
(This program contains
indirect advertisements.)

2
00:00:01,670 --> 00:00:03,310
(All characters, locations,
organizations, and incidents...)

3
00:00:03,310 --> 00:00:04,380
(in this drama are fictional.)

4
00:00:04,440 --> 00:00:05,440
(This production followed
all guidelines for young actors.)

5
00:00:07,080 --> 00:00:08,080
I...

6
00:00:10,220 --> 00:00:11,550
am the one who killed
Joo Sang Cheol.

7
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:13,850
What?

8
00:00:14,350 --> 00:00:15,390
Only now he confessed...

9
00:00:15,990 --> 00:00:17,190
for the first time...

10
00:00:18,260 --> 00:00:19,260
What?

11
00:00:20,290 --> 00:00:21,290
He caused his death?

12
00:00:28,070 --> 00:00:30,700
Mr. Jin Tae Seok,
are you confessing...

13
00:00:31,270 --> 00:00:33,740
to murder right now?

14
00:00:34,340 --> 00:00:35,340
That's right.

15
00:00:35,540 --> 00:00:37,610
To irresponsibly say it...

16
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:39,110
because the statute of limitations
has expired...

17
00:00:39,180 --> 00:00:42,210
Isn't this trial about proving
Cha Ki Beom's innocence?

18
00:00:43,680 --> 00:00:44,680
He is innocent.

19
00:00:47,450 --> 00:00:50,260
The witness's testimony that
the key physical evidence...

20
00:00:50,420 --> 00:00:52,460
presented at the time
was fabricated...

21
00:00:52,790 --> 00:00:55,190
is deemed to be
sufficiently credible.

22
00:00:55,730 --> 00:00:58,030
Therefore,
the previous guilty verdict...

23
00:00:58,460 --> 00:01:01,170
is determined to be based
on an error of fact.

24
00:01:01,670 --> 00:01:04,270
The court will now issue its ruling.

25
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:07,010
The defendant, Cha Ki Beom...

26
00:01:08,070 --> 00:01:09,910
is hereby found not guilty.

27
00:01:27,060 --> 00:01:28,060
(Episode 90)

28
00:01:28,060 --> 00:01:29,960
- He's coming out.
- There they are.

29
00:01:30,030 --> 00:01:32,300
- Regarding future management...
- Are you admitting responsibility?

30
00:01:32,430 --> 00:01:33,430
Is it true?

31
00:01:33,900 --> 00:01:34,900
Did you admit responsibility?

32
00:01:34,970 --> 00:01:38,000
Although the statute has expired,
you confessed to the murder.

33
00:01:38,140 --> 00:01:39,840
This is going to have
enormous repercussions.

34
00:01:40,970 --> 00:01:42,610
What made you come to this decision?

35
00:01:44,910 --> 00:01:48,280
I have been in agony for 25 years.

36
00:01:50,050 --> 00:01:51,620
It may have been a mistake,
but a crime is a crime.

37
00:01:52,450 --> 00:01:54,490
I will spend my life atoning
and dedicate myself...

38
00:01:54,490 --> 00:01:55,490
for Kunhyang's sake,

39
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:58,060
and for the economic development...

40
00:01:59,090 --> 00:02:00,430
of our country.

41
00:02:00,930 --> 00:02:03,390
Do you intend to remain
the group's Honorary Chairman?

42
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:06,430
With a murder confession,
shouldn't you be stepping down?

43
00:02:08,030 --> 00:02:10,600
We'll hold a formal press conference
to provide more details.

44
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:14,310
Just one comment, please!

45
00:02:14,370 --> 00:02:16,810
- Do you have anything to say?
- We'd like a statement, please.

46
00:02:16,810 --> 00:02:19,010
Just one comment, please!

47
00:02:26,450 --> 00:02:27,750
Just one comment, please.

48
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,960
- Just one comment, please.
- Are you admitting it?

49
00:02:33,730 --> 00:02:34,730
Chairman Han Hye Ra.

50
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:41,870
Chairman Han Hye Ra,
how are you feeling?

51
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:46,470
Ms. Cha Jung Won,
you filed for the retrial.

52
00:02:46,470 --> 00:02:47,910
How are you feeling now?

53
00:02:48,770 --> 00:02:50,380
To be able to clear the name...

54
00:02:51,110 --> 00:02:52,740
of the father who raised me...

55
00:02:54,380 --> 00:02:56,210
and restore his honor
makes me so happy.

56
00:02:57,280 --> 00:03:00,080
At the same time,
I can't help but wish...

57
00:03:00,450 --> 00:03:02,820
we could have had this retrial...

58
00:03:03,420 --> 00:03:04,890
while my father was still alive.

59
00:03:06,490 --> 00:03:08,030
It's late, but now at least,

60
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,400
I pray that my father at rest...

61
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:14,400
can finally find some peace.

62
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:20,770
Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul,
how are you feeling right now?

63
00:03:21,610 --> 00:03:23,470
Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok...

64
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:25,740
just confessed
to your father's murder.

65
00:03:26,610 --> 00:03:27,780
For now,

66
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:30,920
I'd like to focus on
the greater importance...

67
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,820
of restoring
Mr. Cha Ki Beom's honor.

68
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,120
As for everything else,

69
00:03:35,020 --> 00:03:37,490
I will release a formal statement
after I've collected my thoughts.

70
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:41,030
- Let's go.
- Look this way, please!

71
00:03:46,130 --> 00:03:48,030
- Give us a comment!
- Was there a reason...

72
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,440
Jung Won, your wish came true.

73
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:54,710
Your dad would be so happy.

74
00:03:55,170 --> 00:03:56,810
This must have been so hard on you.

75
00:03:58,040 --> 00:04:01,450
I know it wasn't easy for you
to even be in the courtroom.

76
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:04,180
That Ki Beom was falsely accused,

77
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,750
and that he died so senselessly...

78
00:04:08,420 --> 00:04:11,620
I can't shake the feeling
it was all my fault.

79
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:15,790
We were able to clear his name
and prove his innocence.

80
00:04:16,060 --> 00:04:17,430
It's all thanks to you, Mom.

81
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:20,130
But I still have so much...

82
00:04:21,570 --> 00:04:22,770
left to atone for.

83
00:04:24,770 --> 00:04:29,070
But why do you think
Jin Tae Seok confessed?

84
00:04:29,810 --> 00:04:32,910
If he was really moved
by what Se Mi said,

85
00:04:33,510 --> 00:04:36,150
does that mean Se Mi
is his Achilles' heel?

86
00:04:37,250 --> 00:04:39,080
He didn't do it for Se Mi.

87
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:45,420
He just wanted to show off
how much he supposedly loves her.

88
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:49,660
It's the same with
how he feels about me.

89
00:04:49,930 --> 00:04:51,730
He wants to tie me down...

90
00:04:52,700 --> 00:04:54,700
and keep me trapped,
one way or another.

91
00:04:54,770 --> 00:04:58,270
But he must know how much
you helped with the retrial.

92
00:04:58,740 --> 00:04:59,970
Is he just going to let it go?

93
00:05:00,770 --> 00:05:02,110
He'll come after me.

94
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,910
Even if it means using you,
Jung Won.

95
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:07,310
Use me?

96
00:05:08,410 --> 00:05:09,480
Jung Won.

97
00:05:10,050 --> 00:05:11,320
This is going to be hard,

98
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,990
but if we're going to
take Jin Tae Seok down,

99
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,090
you and I...

100
00:05:16,820 --> 00:05:18,420
will have to become
enemies for a while.

101
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,730
Enemies?

102
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:27,530
So if we act like enemies,
will he let his guard down?

103
00:05:29,830 --> 00:05:30,940
Exactly.

104
00:05:31,970 --> 00:05:33,200
But before that,

105
00:05:33,710 --> 00:05:37,180
there's something I have to confess.

106
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:41,980
The car accident from 25 years ago.

107
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:45,120
I caused it.

108
00:05:48,250 --> 00:05:49,590
What do you mean?

109
00:05:50,020 --> 00:05:53,690
I could never forgive myself for it.

110
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:58,930
It all started when Jin Tae Seok
gave me that diamond ring.

111
00:06:00,770 --> 00:06:01,930
Ki Beom...

112
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:05,970
couldn't even afford a gold ring.

113
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,270
That's when I realized...

114
00:06:10,110 --> 00:06:11,980
I was a worthless...

115
00:06:13,410 --> 00:06:14,750
and materialistic snob.

116
00:06:16,710 --> 00:06:18,480
And you'd cause an accident
on purpose over that?

117
00:06:19,550 --> 00:06:23,250
- You could have been killed.
- Maybe I wanted to be.

118
00:06:25,460 --> 00:06:27,160
When I opened my eyes,

119
00:06:29,190 --> 00:06:32,030
I wanted to believe it was a permission
from the deities.

120
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:36,230
Permission to abandon you, Su A.

121
00:06:37,570 --> 00:06:41,370
That I didn't have to go on living
as a murderer's wife and...

122
00:06:42,010 --> 00:06:43,170
And what?

123
00:06:43,610 --> 00:06:45,240
I believed Jin Tae Seok's love...

124
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:48,680
was so great
it could move the deities.

125
00:06:50,010 --> 00:06:51,420
Even so, Mom,

126
00:06:51,780 --> 00:06:55,650
you tried to fight your ambition,
even at the risk of your own life.

127
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,420
Now, I sometimes wonder...

128
00:07:00,190 --> 00:07:01,590
If I were in your shoes...

129
00:07:01,990 --> 00:07:03,330
If you were me?

130
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,960
I would've followed
my own ambitions too.

131
00:07:08,930 --> 00:07:13,500
I wouldn't have tried to fight them,
let alone risk my life.

132
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:18,240
I would've made up excuses
about having no choice...

133
00:07:18,980 --> 00:07:20,750
and hidden behind them like armor.

134
00:07:21,310 --> 00:07:22,380
Can you...

135
00:07:24,380 --> 00:07:26,020
forgive me?

136
00:07:28,290 --> 00:07:30,320
Do I have any right to forgive you?

137
00:07:32,190 --> 00:07:33,830
Just like you, Mom,

138
00:07:34,690 --> 00:07:36,330
I was ruled by my ambition.

139
00:07:37,090 --> 00:07:38,500
In fact, maybe even more than you.

140
00:07:45,570 --> 00:07:46,570
Okay.

141
00:07:48,670 --> 00:07:50,470
That's all I need to hear, Jung Won.

142
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,310
Thank you.

143
00:07:56,980 --> 00:07:58,350
So, what do we do now?

144
00:07:58,850 --> 00:08:02,950
Jin Tae Seok will try to divide us
and test us.

145
00:08:03,090 --> 00:08:05,390
We have to do exactly as he says.

146
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,760
Completely.

147
00:08:08,860 --> 00:08:10,160
Be on his side.

148
00:08:13,460 --> 00:08:15,670
See? Everything turned out
just the way you wanted.

149
00:08:16,300 --> 00:08:18,240
That wasn't an easy decision
for me to make.

150
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,840
You didn't really do that...

151
00:08:21,740 --> 00:08:23,540
to Ha Neul's father, did you?

152
00:08:23,610 --> 00:08:26,310
Of course not.
How many times must I tell you?

153
00:08:27,610 --> 00:08:32,380
You felt sorry for Jung Won
and asked me to help clear him.

154
00:08:32,650 --> 00:08:34,020
I did ask you,

155
00:08:34,550 --> 00:08:36,620
but I never thought
you'd actually go through with it.

156
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:41,260
Do you see now
how much I love and cherish you?

157
00:08:53,670 --> 00:08:57,010
What's with his face?
It's all twisted out of shape.

158
00:08:57,210 --> 00:08:59,240
A person's face contorts
when they're deeply moved.

159
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:02,010
So dramatic.

160
00:09:03,450 --> 00:09:06,180
Ha Neul, what now?
You have something to say to me?

161
00:09:06,950 --> 00:09:08,090
Well...

162
00:09:08,090 --> 00:09:11,190
I didn't think you'd actually come.

163
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:14,730
I don't know if that was brave
or just reckless.

164
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:17,560
You can't even say
a simple "thank you."

165
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:19,730
You really take after me.

166
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:25,540
Whatever. I didn't go for you,
so just drop it.

167
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:27,540
I did it so I wouldn't lose face.

168
00:09:28,970 --> 00:09:32,740
Still, why do you think Jin Tae Seok
made a decision like that?

169
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:38,280
I admit I egged him on a little,
but I don't know why he did it.

170
00:09:38,350 --> 00:09:40,550
Probably overconfidence.
Or just plain arrogance.

171
00:09:40,620 --> 00:09:43,550
Right. Who would dare
to cross Jin Tae Seok?

172
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:45,020
The statute of limitations ran out,

173
00:09:45,020 --> 00:09:47,190
so he must have thought,
"So what are you going to do about it?"

174
00:09:48,190 --> 00:09:51,000
Or, Se Mi might have played
a more important part in it.

175
00:09:53,430 --> 00:09:57,770
- Se Mi convinced Jin Tae Seok? How?
- I'm not sure myself.

176
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:00,710
And even if I knew,
I couldn't tell you.

177
00:10:03,110 --> 00:10:06,240
So Jin Se Mi has Jin Tae Seok
wrapped around her little finger.

178
00:10:07,850 --> 00:10:10,180
Let's eat. Ha Neul,
have a bite before you go.

179
00:10:10,250 --> 00:10:13,080
- Let's eat.
- Sounds good.

180
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:23,030
Hey, it's not like
I just got out of jail.

181
00:10:23,090 --> 00:10:25,430
What's with this huge spread of tofu?

182
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:28,070
You confessed in court, didn't you?

183
00:10:28,370 --> 00:10:30,030
This is special tofu to commend you.

184
00:10:30,100 --> 00:10:31,400
Grandma prepared it.

185
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,600
Let me try.

186
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:41,280
- This is good.
- She loves dissing me, right?

187
00:10:41,350 --> 00:10:43,050
She says you're right.

188
00:10:45,180 --> 00:10:47,450
How could you serve tofu every day?

189
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:50,320
It's not like I was haunted
by a ghost who died craving tofu.

190
00:10:50,890 --> 00:10:53,960
Don't even say tofu to me again.
I'm not eating it!

191
00:10:54,130 --> 00:10:55,160
Hey, you!

192
00:10:56,690 --> 00:10:57,760
You startled me.

193
00:10:58,460 --> 00:11:00,260
- My little baby.
- Oh my!

194
00:11:00,330 --> 00:11:01,900
Just have one little bite.

195
00:11:03,770 --> 00:11:07,140
I'm giving you this
so you can live a pure, clean life.

196
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:13,210
It's actually good. But Grandma,
I was already pure and fair-skinned.

197
00:11:13,580 --> 00:11:15,250
I just didn't live that way.

198
00:11:15,310 --> 00:11:19,650
That's why you need to eat more tofu
and turn over a new leaf.

199
00:11:19,750 --> 00:11:22,320
Turn over a new leaf?
Leaf? Is that a person's name?

200
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:25,190
It is white and pure.

201
00:11:25,260 --> 00:11:27,120
It makes you feel
all warm and fuzzy.

202
00:11:27,530 --> 00:11:30,160
Cut the "warm and fuzzy."
I absolutely hate it.

203
00:11:34,330 --> 00:11:37,000
Hey! Why are you eating standing up?
Were you raised in a barn?

204
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,400
Sit down and eat.

205
00:11:46,980 --> 00:11:50,920
- I should thank you, I suppose?
- Of course you should.

206
00:11:51,650 --> 00:11:55,490
I braved public condemnation
to prove Cha Ki Beom's innocence.

207
00:11:56,450 --> 00:11:58,560
It wouldn't have been easy
without my testimony, would it?

208
00:12:02,090 --> 00:12:03,930
Are you trying to play the hero now?

209
00:12:04,460 --> 00:12:07,630
Does that erase the fact
that you killed my father?

210
00:12:08,370 --> 00:12:09,730
I am your father.

211
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:14,240
Act like the eldest daughter
of the Kunhyang family.

212
00:12:14,770 --> 00:12:17,310
Throw away that wretched
past of yours.

213
00:12:17,610 --> 00:12:19,140
Wretched?

214
00:12:19,340 --> 00:12:23,880
How desperate must Hye Ra have been
to fake a car crash 25 years ago?

215
00:12:25,220 --> 00:12:29,350
It must have been awful for her
to abandon her daughter at seven.

216
00:12:30,890 --> 00:12:31,890
What did you just say?

217
00:12:33,060 --> 00:12:34,060
She staged it?

218
00:12:37,800 --> 00:12:38,800
My dear daughter.

219
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:43,130
Do you still not know
what kind of woman your mother is?

220
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:46,700
That's ridiculous.
I'm going to go ask my mother...

221
00:12:46,940 --> 00:12:49,210
It's true.
She staged the whole thing.

222
00:12:50,710 --> 00:12:52,440
I'm the one who helped her.

223
00:12:54,980 --> 00:12:56,880
I tried to talk her out of it,
but she wouldn't listen.

224
00:12:56,950 --> 00:13:00,650
She did it so that
she could be with Chairman Jin.

225
00:13:00,650 --> 00:13:01,650
No.

226
00:13:03,420 --> 00:13:04,760
That can't be true.

227
00:13:05,090 --> 00:13:07,290
Secretary Yoon was
Hye Ra's right-hand woman.

228
00:13:07,890 --> 00:13:09,160
You need to accept the truth
when you hear it.

229
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:14,270
To the point of risking
her own life,

230
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:17,840
did she want to be part
of a tycoon family that badly?

231
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:28,250
I can't forgive her.

232
00:13:28,250 --> 00:13:29,350
Never.

233
00:14:01,210 --> 00:14:02,350
Jung Won.

234
00:14:03,210 --> 00:14:05,280
Now that the retrial is over,

235
00:14:06,880 --> 00:14:10,150
the father who raised you
has been proven innocent.

236
00:14:12,060 --> 00:14:13,290
It's all thanks to your father here.

237
00:14:17,390 --> 00:14:18,460
From now on...

238
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:23,000
I'd like you to cut ties...

239
00:14:23,830 --> 00:14:25,000
with Jo Mi Hyang.

240
00:14:26,370 --> 00:14:27,570
That's a good idea.

241
00:14:28,210 --> 00:14:30,070
Cha Ki Beom's been proven innocent.

242
00:14:30,070 --> 00:14:31,280
You've done your part, right?

243
00:14:31,910 --> 00:14:34,780
I heard you opened that restaurant
for Jo Mi Hyang, Jung Won.

244
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:43,920
- I'm sorry, I should have told you.
- Unbelievable.

245
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:45,520
How much did you squirrel away...

246
00:14:45,520 --> 00:14:46,760
as a fake daughter-in-law
of a tycoon family...

247
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:49,530
to open a place for Jo Mi Hyang?
She's not even your real mother.

248
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:52,530
What a crude way to talk,
especially in front of your elders.

249
00:14:53,660 --> 00:14:55,330
Why are you picking on Young Chae?

250
00:14:55,700 --> 00:14:57,170
It's not like she said
anything out of line.

251
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:02,810
- Jung Won.
- Stop it!

252
00:15:03,970 --> 00:15:05,410
I said,
stop with your hypocritical act.

253
00:15:09,550 --> 00:15:10,710
What did you just say?

254
00:15:10,780 --> 00:15:14,150
I almost fell for
your whole "I had no choice" act.

255
00:15:14,490 --> 00:15:15,720
I actually almost believed you.

256
00:15:17,420 --> 00:15:19,120
Why are you acting like this?

257
00:15:19,890 --> 00:15:22,630
I'm so sick of it! The endless lies!

258
00:15:23,130 --> 00:15:25,160
It's like a broken record.

259
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:28,200
And you're telling me to cut ties
with the mother who raised me?

260
00:15:28,700 --> 00:15:31,070
No! I could never do that!

261
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:33,570
Do you have any idea
how selfish you are?

262
00:15:34,310 --> 00:15:37,610
- I wish I'd just died back then!
- Jung Won.

263
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:40,340
How could you say
something so horrible?

264
00:15:40,610 --> 00:15:42,610
How could you say that you wish
you were dead in front of your mother?

265
00:15:43,450 --> 00:15:45,180
Do you have any idea
how hurtful that is?

266
00:15:50,150 --> 00:15:52,360
As if anyone would believe
that you're actually hurt.

267
00:15:52,790 --> 00:15:55,290
You're a natural
at lying and deceiving people.

268
00:15:56,790 --> 00:15:59,160
You knew from the beginning
I wasn't his daughter, didn't you?

269
00:16:00,030 --> 00:16:02,470
To think you married him
while you were pregnant with me...

270
00:16:03,100 --> 00:16:04,400
It's despicable.

271
00:16:06,270 --> 00:16:07,370
Mom!

272
00:16:08,270 --> 00:16:09,770
How could you say that?

273
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:19,720
Jung Won.

274
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:22,590
Honey, calm down.

275
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:38,940
This family is a complete mess.

276
00:16:39,570 --> 00:16:41,040
It's an absolute war zone.

277
00:16:42,340 --> 00:16:46,540
- Are you sure you can win this war?
- Right now, the internet...

278
00:16:46,980 --> 00:16:49,680
is blowing up with accusations
that Chairman Jin is a murderer.

279
00:16:50,880 --> 00:16:53,780
Step down as Honorary Chairman.

280
00:16:53,780 --> 00:16:55,190
So I should step down...

281
00:16:55,850 --> 00:16:57,620
and make you Chairman?

282
00:16:57,620 --> 00:17:02,460
Only I can keep Chairman Gong
and Vice Chairman Joo in check.

283
00:17:02,590 --> 00:17:03,960
That's what will save Kunhyang.

284
00:17:04,030 --> 00:17:05,430
I'm telling you, it's the only way.

285
00:17:07,260 --> 00:17:08,330
What's so funny?

286
00:17:08,730 --> 00:17:11,800
I can see the wheels turning
in that little head of yours.

287
00:17:18,180 --> 00:17:19,940
So, is he going to
make you Chairman?

288
00:17:20,610 --> 00:17:21,880
He won't give me a straight answer.

289
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:25,280
So he knows after all.

290
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:26,920
Know what?

291
00:17:28,450 --> 00:17:29,750
It's nothing. Never mind.

292
00:17:30,090 --> 00:17:32,090
I'll get my father to agree,
one way or another.

293
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:35,790
I can't let Cha Jung Won
and Joo Ha Neul get it.

294
00:17:35,790 --> 00:17:36,890
Of course not.

295
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:40,130
Kunhyang Group belongs to you,
no matter what anyone says.

296
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:41,570
That's how it's meant to be.

297
00:17:45,570 --> 00:17:46,570
What is it?

298
00:17:48,840 --> 00:17:50,270
Do I look pretty today or something?

299
00:17:52,580 --> 00:17:55,310
- You're unbelievable.
- What?

300
00:17:56,050 --> 00:17:59,850
I was so cruel to you
and even threw you out...

301
00:18:01,450 --> 00:18:04,590
Se Hoon, you feel bad, don't you?

302
00:18:05,260 --> 00:18:06,320
What?

303
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,760
Who said I was sorry?

304
00:18:13,600 --> 00:18:14,630
What was that?

305
00:18:15,070 --> 00:18:16,970
Did Jin Se Hoon really
just fall for me?

306
00:18:22,940 --> 00:18:26,680
By the way, why did Cha Jung Won
suddenly lash out at her own mother?

307
00:18:27,210 --> 00:18:28,880
I thought they were
thick as thieves.

308
00:18:39,790 --> 00:18:42,160
I need to get the password
for that Swiss account.

309
00:18:44,090 --> 00:18:45,530
It's my only lifeline.

310
00:18:52,700 --> 00:18:53,840
You told Jung Won...

311
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:56,040
about the accident
all those years ago?

312
00:18:56,310 --> 00:18:58,910
I'm sorry.
I had no choice but to tell her.

313
00:19:00,410 --> 00:19:01,550
It's my fault.

314
00:19:02,710 --> 00:19:05,780
This is the price I pay
for my choice.

315
00:19:06,380 --> 00:19:07,380
Now...

316
00:19:07,920 --> 00:19:09,990
Jung Won...

317
00:19:10,750 --> 00:19:12,820
will never forgive me.

318
00:19:34,380 --> 00:19:36,080
This is a surprise.

319
00:19:36,680 --> 00:19:38,620
You're calling me first
for a change.

320
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:41,080
All chaos is breaking loose
at the Kunhyang house.

321
00:19:41,390 --> 00:19:43,190
Chairman Han slapped Cha Jung Won.

322
00:19:43,290 --> 00:19:46,690
What? But I thought they were
getting along so well.

323
00:19:46,760 --> 00:19:48,460
I know, right?
She must've lost her mind.

324
00:19:48,690 --> 00:19:52,200
By the way, are you going to stay
with Jin Se Hoon?

325
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:55,570
You should be divorcing him.

326
00:19:55,570 --> 00:19:58,170
He's all flash.
Why should you be with him?

327
00:19:58,240 --> 00:20:01,270
There you go again.
I'll live my own life.

328
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:04,140
Nothing ever worked out
when I listened to you.

329
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:07,140
I like Jin Se Hoon.

330
00:20:07,610 --> 00:20:09,710
I don't care
he's not Jin Tae Seok's real son.

331
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:12,220
Wait, does Jin Se Hoon know...

332
00:20:12,220 --> 00:20:14,320
that he's not
Jin Tae Seok's biological son?

333
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:15,490
He doesn't know.

334
00:20:15,550 --> 00:20:18,420
No, he can't ever find out.

335
00:20:19,820 --> 00:20:20,990
He doesn't know?

336
00:20:24,360 --> 00:20:27,430
What am I going to do
with Young Chae?

337
00:20:27,860 --> 00:20:29,070
You're home?

338
00:20:29,670 --> 00:20:30,730
What's wrong with Young Chae?

339
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:33,200
Is she divorcing Se Hoon...

340
00:20:33,200 --> 00:20:35,040
because he's not
Jin Tae Seok's biological son?

341
00:20:35,470 --> 00:20:39,710
If that were true, I wouldn't worry.
She's pretending they have a future,

342
00:20:39,780 --> 00:20:43,010
- and that's the bigger problem.
- Maybe Young Chae has grown up.

343
00:20:43,550 --> 00:20:46,380
She's not being calculating
and is choosing Se Hoon for love.

344
00:20:46,450 --> 00:20:49,320
You're being naive.
You have no idea.

345
00:20:49,690 --> 00:20:52,920
It seems Han Hye Ra and Cha Jung Won
are on the outs again.

346
00:20:52,990 --> 00:20:54,190
Do you know anything about it?

347
00:20:55,090 --> 00:20:56,190
On the outs? What do you mean?

348
00:20:58,100 --> 00:20:59,530
A staged car accident?

349
00:21:00,830 --> 00:21:03,030
How could she do
something like that?

350
00:21:03,900 --> 00:21:07,300
To risk her own life
and gamble her future like that.

351
00:21:07,370 --> 00:21:09,070
Have you tried looking at it
another way?

352
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:15,410
That's how desperate she was
not to lose Su A.

353
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:20,520
Right, I had the same thought
as you, Ha Neul.

354
00:21:21,590 --> 00:21:24,090
My mother was so desperate
to live...

355
00:21:24,820 --> 00:21:26,620
that she was willing
to risk her own life.

356
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,560
Now I can understand.

357
00:21:30,530 --> 00:21:32,360
I'd only just forgiven my mother,

358
00:21:33,930 --> 00:21:35,870
and now, in front of Jin Tae Seok,

359
00:21:36,730 --> 00:21:38,800
I have to pretend to hate her
all over again.

360
00:21:41,070 --> 00:21:42,340
What are you thinking about?

361
00:21:42,810 --> 00:21:44,010
Ha Neul.

362
00:21:44,710 --> 00:21:46,710
- Do you trust me?
- Of course I do.

363
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:50,250
- Everything I say?
- Absolutely.

364
00:21:50,710 --> 00:21:51,720
Why?

365
00:21:53,950 --> 00:21:55,190
Because I love you.

366
00:22:10,670 --> 00:22:11,740
What's this for?

367
00:22:12,300 --> 00:22:15,410
So I can get wasted and pass out?

368
00:22:16,270 --> 00:22:17,470
This is for a celebration.

369
00:22:18,180 --> 00:22:19,380
What's there to celebrate?

370
00:22:21,850 --> 00:22:25,550
Hearing that Ki Beom
was found innocent...

371
00:22:26,250 --> 00:22:28,790
feels like a ten-year weight
has been lifted.

372
00:22:31,620 --> 00:22:35,660
But Ki Beom himself isn't here
to see it.

373
00:22:37,690 --> 00:22:39,330
I'm sure he was watching.

374
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:44,970
And I'm sure he was very pleased.

375
00:22:46,770 --> 00:22:48,000
Manager Hwang.

376
00:22:48,540 --> 00:22:50,940
You're someone
I just can't figure out.

377
00:22:52,410 --> 00:22:55,310
You're so thoughtful,
but why did you...

378
00:22:58,880 --> 00:23:00,680
Don't tell me
you started without us.

379
00:23:01,180 --> 00:23:03,650
Look who's here!
It's our Vice Chairman.

380
00:23:05,890 --> 00:23:08,190
Mom, what about me? Am I invisible?

381
00:23:08,790 --> 00:23:11,190
Of course I see you.
I'm so proud of you, sweetheart.

382
00:23:11,900 --> 00:23:15,600
- You worked hard too, Mom.
- Oh, please. I didn't do anything.

383
00:23:16,100 --> 00:23:19,240
Now Ki Beom
can rest a little easier.

384
00:23:19,370 --> 00:23:21,940
- It's all thanks to you, Jung Won.
- This is just the beginning.

385
00:23:23,340 --> 00:23:25,810
We have to expose the truth
of Cha Ki Beom's unjust death.

386
00:23:26,040 --> 00:23:27,440
And I will.

387
00:23:28,350 --> 00:23:31,650
Do you really think
that Jin Tae Seok will just confess?

388
00:23:32,820 --> 00:23:34,750
Whatever it takes,

389
00:23:35,550 --> 00:23:36,550
I have to see this through.

390
00:23:36,690 --> 00:23:40,820
All right, but before all that,
to celebrate today's victory,

391
00:23:41,060 --> 00:23:42,930
let's all have a celebratory drink.

392
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:45,200
Sounds great.

393
00:23:49,600 --> 00:23:50,600
I'd love to.

394
00:23:55,970 --> 00:23:56,970
All right.

395
00:23:57,270 --> 00:23:59,880
Let's save our worries for tomorrow.
Tonight, we drink.

396
00:24:10,190 --> 00:24:12,760
This one is for you, Ki Beom.

397
00:24:14,460 --> 00:24:15,460
Let's make a toast.

398
00:24:16,090 --> 00:24:17,090
Cheers.

399
00:24:29,540 --> 00:24:31,540
(Kunhyang Group)

400
00:24:45,360 --> 00:24:50,360
(Cha Jung Won)

401
00:24:52,200 --> 00:24:54,760
Are you happy now, Cha Jung Won?

402
00:24:55,530 --> 00:24:56,670
You think you've won?

403
00:24:57,270 --> 00:24:59,740
Cha Jung Won,
why meddle in my life...

404
00:25:01,170 --> 00:25:02,640
and get in my way at every turn?

405
00:25:04,170 --> 00:25:05,280
You awful witch.

406
00:25:13,980 --> 00:25:15,990
Acting all high and mighty...

407
00:25:15,990 --> 00:25:17,290
just because they think they're
the only ones with Kunhyang blood...

408
00:25:17,550 --> 00:25:19,690
(Cha Jung Won)

409
00:25:25,300 --> 00:25:26,660
Go on.
Fight like you're sworn enemies.

410
00:25:31,570 --> 00:25:33,070
You didn't forget
the walking practice, right?

411
00:25:33,070 --> 00:25:34,240
Of course not.

412
00:25:37,570 --> 00:25:38,580
What in the world...

413
00:25:40,240 --> 00:25:42,510
(Cha Jung Won)

414
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:43,680
Who would do something like this?

415
00:25:45,220 --> 00:25:46,350
What now?

416
00:25:47,180 --> 00:25:49,090
The show's tomorrow.

417
00:25:51,320 --> 00:25:52,390
What's going on?

418
00:25:57,460 --> 00:25:58,460
Why are you all staring at me
like that?

419
00:26:01,930 --> 00:26:04,270
Cha Jung Won,
have you finally lost your mind?

420
00:26:04,670 --> 00:26:08,540
- Why would you cut up the clothes?
- I know. I guess I've lost my mind.

421
00:26:10,540 --> 00:26:11,710
What's going on?

422
00:26:13,580 --> 00:26:16,080
Don't tell me
it was Director Jin again.

423
00:26:16,950 --> 00:26:18,010
What did you say?

424
00:26:18,010 --> 00:26:20,650
Did tearing up the sketch
not satisfy you?

425
00:26:21,750 --> 00:26:22,750
Right.

426
00:26:24,090 --> 00:26:25,190
(Jin Se Mi)

427
00:26:25,290 --> 00:26:26,290
Is that what you used?

428
00:26:27,420 --> 00:26:29,560
- Joo Young Chae.
- Young Chae, we need to talk.

429
00:26:31,730 --> 00:26:34,260
Talk about what?
Stop being arrogant.

430
00:26:42,670 --> 00:26:45,010
- What's wrong with you?
- Jung Won.

431
00:26:45,080 --> 00:26:46,540
I have nothing to say to you.

432
00:26:47,540 --> 00:26:50,110
You staged this, you hypocrite!

433
00:26:59,790 --> 00:27:02,060
(Chairman Gong Nan Sook)

434
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:14,440
What are these?

435
00:27:16,310 --> 00:27:18,580
(Probability of a blood relationship
is estimated at 0.123 percent)

436
00:27:22,550 --> 00:27:24,610
(Probability of a blood relationship
is estimated at 99.998 percent)

437
00:27:27,680 --> 00:27:28,890
Which one is real?

438
00:27:29,750 --> 00:27:31,490
One is what Young Chae gave me,

439
00:27:31,590 --> 00:27:34,760
and the other one
was hidden in her bag.

440
00:27:35,290 --> 00:27:39,200
Are you saying Young Chae
lied to you?

441
00:27:40,900 --> 00:27:45,240
Se Hoon, it turns out you are not
Jin Tae Seok's biological son.

442
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:47,140
Young Chae knew
and tried to keep it a secret.

443
00:27:47,140 --> 00:27:48,410
That can't be true.

444
00:27:49,270 --> 00:27:50,570
You're trying to trick me,
aren't you?

445
00:27:50,710 --> 00:27:53,110
Jin Tae Seok probably
knew it all along.

446
00:27:53,180 --> 00:27:56,710
My father raised me
to be the heir to Kunhyang.

447
00:27:56,980 --> 00:28:00,280
He was harsher and stricter with me
than anyone else!

448
00:28:00,350 --> 00:28:04,420
Jin Tae Seok wanted a loyal dog
who'd live and die on his command...

449
00:28:04,490 --> 00:28:06,760
more than he wanted a real son.

450
00:28:06,760 --> 00:28:07,760
No!

451
00:28:10,190 --> 00:28:11,730
My father trusted me.

452
00:28:12,530 --> 00:28:13,600
He may have seemed cold...

453
00:28:13,660 --> 00:28:17,270
Come on, you had to believe
you were his real son...

454
00:28:17,470 --> 00:28:21,040
so that you'd bark obediently
whenever your master ordered, right?

455
00:28:21,270 --> 00:28:23,870
And you played that part perfectly.

456
00:28:24,970 --> 00:28:28,810
My father used me?

457
00:28:28,910 --> 00:28:31,410
You were fooled by Jin Tae Seok...

458
00:28:31,410 --> 00:28:32,720
and Young Chae.

459
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:35,920
Young Chae...

460
00:28:37,290 --> 00:28:39,420
probably did it to protect me.

461
00:28:40,060 --> 00:28:42,060
You still don't know her at all.

462
00:28:43,860 --> 00:28:47,060
She would've been scared of losing
her place in the Kunhyang family...

463
00:28:47,330 --> 00:28:51,700
if it had come out that you weren't
Jin Tae Seok's real son.

464
00:28:51,700 --> 00:28:52,700
It's so obvious.

465
00:28:55,140 --> 00:28:59,040
Young Chae was in love
with your background.

466
00:28:59,480 --> 00:29:00,540
Don't kid yourself.

467
00:29:22,130 --> 00:29:23,330
It's not true, is it?

468
00:29:23,330 --> 00:29:25,240
That I'm not your biological son.

469
00:29:25,840 --> 00:29:27,140
I can't believe it.

470
00:29:27,600 --> 00:29:29,270
Who's been feeding you that garbage?

471
00:29:29,440 --> 00:29:31,470
You're the one who's lying,
aren't you?

472
00:29:32,780 --> 00:29:36,610
Chairman Gong Nan Sook
showed me the DNA test results.

473
00:29:36,710 --> 00:29:37,850
I'm telling you, it's not true.

474
00:29:40,650 --> 00:29:41,650
It's true.

475
00:29:42,990 --> 00:29:43,990
Se Hoon.

476
00:29:46,460 --> 00:29:47,860
You're not his biological son.

477
00:29:48,560 --> 00:29:50,190
How would you know that,
Chairman Han?

478
00:29:50,390 --> 00:29:51,660
I confirmed it myself.

479
00:29:54,060 --> 00:29:55,570
What's going on, Father?

480
00:29:58,330 --> 00:29:59,340
It's true.

481
00:29:59,900 --> 00:30:02,010
Se Hoon,
you are not my flesh and blood.

482
00:30:05,440 --> 00:30:07,040
Then who is my father?

483
00:30:07,240 --> 00:30:09,350
Your late mother
was seeing another man.

484
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:11,410
He is your father.

485
00:30:15,290 --> 00:30:19,620
You never had any right
to be the heir to Kunhyang Group.

486
00:30:19,890 --> 00:30:23,430
And Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok
knew it all along.

487
00:30:25,300 --> 00:30:27,800
Is that true, Father?

488
00:30:28,870 --> 00:30:31,130
We'll talk later.
I know you're confused now.

489
00:30:48,450 --> 00:30:49,550
When did you find out?

490
00:30:50,190 --> 00:30:51,190
Recently.

491
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:54,460
But my father knew from the start,
didn't he?

492
00:30:56,190 --> 00:30:59,200
From the moment I was born.

493
00:30:59,860 --> 00:31:00,860
Most likely.

494
00:31:01,930 --> 00:31:03,300
Right now you're probably thinking,

495
00:31:04,170 --> 00:31:05,400
"Okay, Jin Se Hoon,"

496
00:31:06,340 --> 00:31:08,870
"you're out of the running
to be Kunhyang's heir."

497
00:31:09,870 --> 00:31:11,110
That's what you're thinking, right?

498
00:31:18,350 --> 00:31:21,850
I've just realized that as far as
Jin Tae Seok is concerned,

499
00:31:23,020 --> 00:31:24,150
you were already out of the picture.

500
00:31:24,450 --> 00:31:26,520
Do you think I'm going to
back down just like that?

501
00:31:27,990 --> 00:31:29,890
I won't go down without a fight.

502
00:31:30,990 --> 00:31:32,000
Just you wait.

503
00:31:42,610 --> 00:31:44,040
You wanted to see me?

504
00:31:46,940 --> 00:31:47,940
Han Hye Ra.

505
00:31:48,950 --> 00:31:51,650
Take her down
from the chairman's seat.

506
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:53,920
Excuse me?

507
00:31:54,280 --> 00:31:56,450
If you do that, I'll acknowledge you
as my daughter.

508
00:31:57,590 --> 00:31:59,620
And I might even consider you
my heir.

509
00:32:14,500 --> 00:32:17,540
